The paper discusses the testing and evaluation of deep neural networks, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses attacks on DNNs, which falls under the category of cybersecurity (cs.CR). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of DNNs in various applications such as face recognition and autonomous car control, which falls under the categories of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and computer vision (cs.CV). Finally, the paper discusses the implementation and benchmarking of DNN testing, which falls under the category of software engineering (cs.SE).
